Class Erraneous

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
Datastructures.Results.Result
Datastructures.Results.Erraneous
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Erraneous extends Result
This class represents results of erraneous SAT-algorithms. They deliver a model which still makes some clauses false. Created by ohlbach on 11.10.2018.
